title: The Alhambra (Wonders of Man - Art Architecture Ebook)
description:
pdf / English / 1974 / 172 pages / 43.6 MB / ISBN 10 0882250876

A brilliant kaleidoscope of shimmering grace, the Alhambra is the last and finest Muslim monument in Spain. Although built at the ebb tide of Islam's Iberian influence, it epitomizes all the tumultuous years of conquest and reconquest that were characteristic of Spain under the Muslims
